      "content": {
        "title": "Regional Classification Systems",
        "definition": "Anatomic-region schemes including Neer (proximal humerus), Garden (femoral neck), Gustilo (open fractures), and Schatzker (tibial plateau).",
        "summary": "Regional classifications guide operative indication and prognosis within specific anatomic areas."
